    Using SPL_autoload in PHP.
    New keywords to automate the SPL_autoload function in the implementation process,
This function is intended to be used as a default implementation for __autoload().
If nothing else is specified and spl_autoload_register() is called without any
parameters then this functions will be used for any later call to __autoload().

    Using custom __autoload replace __autoload by default, automatically loaded from
the directory of the file.Use this procedure in a project TBP
(http://github.com/wackonline/tbp), autoloader instance also can be run completely.